# Python — ONE stable interpreter for a base install (decision 2026-06-06:
# one version per language kit-wide, a step or two behind latest for
# stability). 3.12 aligns with .configs setup.sh (PYTHON_VERSION=3.12.11).
# Prefix resolves to the latest 3.12.x at install time.
# Project envs rebuild per-project; pip freezes archived in snapshot/languages/.
3.12

